BookTok Promotion

Strategic marketing campaigns that connect your book with passionate readers on TikTok

What is BookTok?

BookTok is TikTok's massive book community - a space where millions of readers discover, discuss, and fall in love with books every single day. It's one of the most influential book marketing platforms in recent years.

Videos tagged #BookTok have garnered billions of views, making it a powerhouse for driving book sales and creating bestsellers. Authors who tap into this community see remarkable results.

We understand what makes BookTok tick. We know the trends, the tropes readers love, and how to position your book for maximum visibility and authentic engagement.

About Green Marbles

Your trusted partner in the journey from manuscript to reader

Our Story

Green Marbles PR & Publishing was founded with a simple mission: to help authors navigate the complex world of book promotion and publishing. We understand that writing a book is just the beginning of the journey.

Our team combines expertise in digital marketing, traditional publishing, and the ever-evolving landscape of BookTok to offer comprehensive support for authors at every stage.

We believe every story deserves to find its readers. That's why we take a personalized approach with each author, understanding their unique voice and goals to create strategies that truly work.
